You let Hwang Jeongyeon do that to us?

711
01:04:32,589 --> 01:04:34,489
If you want, I could get rid of her.

712
01:04:34,596 --> 01:04:36,624
If things go according
to Jo Pilyeon's plans,

713
01:04:36,734 --> 01:04:39,174
<i>our fight will become even harder.</i>

714
